## `umount_cmd(args) -> int`
<!-- checksum: fuse-cli-3 -->

### Implementation Notes

```python
def umount_cmd(args):
    from sqlite_fs.fuse import umount
    try:
        umount(args.mountpoint)
        return 0
    except Exception as e:
        sys.stderr.write(f"sqlite-fs: umount failed: {e}\n")
        return 1
```

